    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document provides a general framework for describing network traffic flows, presents an architecture for traffic flow measurement and reporting, discusses how this relates to an overall network traffic flow architecture and indicates how it can be used within the Internet.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
